    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Immediate/rapid\nhearing loss\nor hearing loss upon awakening\nMostly unilateral hearing loss\nSensation of blocked or full ear, patient doesn’t recognize hearing is gone\nDifficulty in localizing sound\nTinnitus\nis common\nSome patients report\nvertigo\nOccasionally\near pain\nis present\nNo sign of obstruction or\notitis media\non physical exam",
